description:
6-panel Mosaic of the Milky Way Core

Canon 50mm f/1.8 "Nifty Fifty", Canon 600D/T3i

2019-07-03 120×30sec ISO1600 f/4 - Dark Horse Nebula
2019-07-06 43×30sec@ISO1600 f/3.2 - Lagoon Nebula
2019-07-07 28×45sec@ISO1600 f/4 - Sagittarius Star Cloud
2019-07-26 80×45sec ISO1600 f/4 - Omega Nebula
2019-07-26 80×45sec@ISO1600 f/4 - Prawn Nebula
2019-07-27/28 29×45sec@ISO1600 f/4 - Antares
Spherical projection, galactic coordinate system

Present are Jupiter, the Omega, Eagle, Lagoon, Trifid, Lobster, Cat's Paw, Prawn, and Prancing Horse Nebulas, the Great Sagittarius Star Cloud, the Small Sagittarius Star Cloud, the Great Rift, and the rotation axis of the Milky Way galaxy.

Tropic of Capricorn, Northern Territory, Australia.
title: Mosaic of the Milky Way Core
